Name: red_sky
AboutMe:
I'm presently a Computer Science major at Pennsylvania State University's University Park campus. The course load is rather difficult, but I enjoy it nonetheless. I enjoy programming in my spare time. I have a ton of side projects, many of which I haven't ever finished. My language of choice is C#. I've been using C# since I was 12-13. Aside from C#, I also have experience in Java, C/C++, perl, python, HTML/CSS, javascript, and some VB.Net.

Outside of the programming world, I also heavily enjoy music. It's one of my favorite things. I listen to essentially everything. At the last check, I had about 80 genres in my collection.

I love technology, especially in the mobile sense. I think all of the advancements brought by Apple, Google, Microsoft, Palm, and the others are phenomenal. I have a Nexus 4 and love it to death. Every day, I find new things I can do with it. Aside from that, I find it really cool to develop on mobile platforms.
